{"word":"στεγνός","slug":"στεγνός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>στεγνός</b></el> <el>(στεγνός, ή, όν) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:contracted, contraction'>contr.</a> from <a href='S:στεγανός'><el>στεγανός</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>waterproof</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>; <el>στεγνὰ οἰκήματα</el>, of a cave, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>as <a href='S:Substantive'>Subst.</a>, <el>στεγνόν, οῦ</el>, <i>a covered dwelling</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}